{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025180/extras/clip2.gif?t=1733877003\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SYNOPSIS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <strong>La Salamanca</strong>, you put yourself in the shoes of a young man from Argentina, who after the mysterious disappearance of all his friends during a trip to Santiago del Estero, will have to look for them in their supposed meeting place: An old and dark apartment complex called <i>&quot;El Portal&quot;</i>, a &quot;cozy&quot; place, which is not really what it seems...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Inspired by a local legend from Argentina</strong>, you will have to descend deeper and deeper into this place straight out of hell, <strong>running and hiding from its abominations</strong>, to finally reveal the truth of what happened with your colleagues, and what this site is truly hiding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025180/extras/clip6.gif?t=1733877003\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  A <strong>psychological horror game</strong> that immerses you in a story <strong>inspired by a legend from the north of Argentina.</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  A <strong>thrilling atmosphere</strong>\u00a0that will keep even the bravest on their toes throughout the game. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  <strong>An episodic structure</strong> where each chapter and level will <strong>have different approaches in their mechanics</strong> to differentiate themselves from each other.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  <strong>Multiple puzzles</strong> to sharpen your brain as you <strong>progress through the story and evade monsters.</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  <strong>Terrifying monsters and demons</strong>, where you must <strong>develop different tactics</strong> to deal with each of them <strong>based on their behavior and the environment around you.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025180/extras/clip1.gif?t=1733877003\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MADE IN ARGENTINA</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We are <strong>Carpincho Studio</strong>, a bunch of young amateur devs from Argentina (Mostly from Rosario). We love games and both playing and developing them is our passion, reason why we decided, as a group, to finally make public our first ever game, <strong>&quot;La Salamanca&quot;</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We also love Capybaras. Best animal ever.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3025180?t=1733877003","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025180/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1733877003","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025180/cfaeac2f610e3bfce37817630513f82502864209/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733877003","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025180/cfaeac2f610e3bfce37817630513f82502864209/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733877003","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Captions available","id":13}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"\"La Salamanca\" may containt content not apropiate for all ages, containing Frequent Violence or Gore, Strong Horror Themes, Strong Language, and General Mature Content."},"demos":[{"appid":3027520,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_parag